   "endLine": 393,
   "source": "<ROUTINE I-DRAGON-EYE (\"OPTIONAL\" (GARG <>))\n %<DEBUG-CODE <COND (<OR ,IDEBUG <==? .GARG ,G-DEBUG>>\n\t\t     <TELL \"[I-DRAGON-EYE:\">\n\t\t     <COND (<==? .GARG ,G-DEBUG> <RFALSE>)>)>>\n <COND (<ZERO? <GETB ,LAST-NAME 0>>\n\t;<NOT <L? ,DRAGON-EYE-COLOR 0>>\n\t<PERFORM ,V?PUSH ,DRAGON-EYE>\n\t<RFATAL>)>>"
