   "source": "<ROUTINE WILLING? (PER \"OPT\" (KISS <>))\n <COND (<ZERO? .KISS>\n\t<COND (<L? ,BED-TIME ,PRESENT-TIME>\n\t       <RFALSE>)\n\t      (<QUEUED? ,I-TOUR>\n\t       <RFALSE>)\n\t      (<OR <EQUAL? ,HERE ,DINING-ROOM>\n\t\t   <QUEUED? ,I-DINNER-SIT> ;\"not during dinner\">\n\t       <RFALSE>)\n\t      (<EQUAL? .PER ,CONFESSED ,CAPTOR>\n\t       <RFALSE>)\n\t      (T <RTRUE>)>)\n       (<EQUAL? .PER ,FRIEND>\n\t<COND (<NOT <EQUAL? ,VARIATION ,FRIEND-C>>\n\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t      (T <RFALSE>)>)\n       (<EQUAL? .PER ,BUTLER>\n\t<COND (<AND <VERB? EMPTY ;\"UNPACK\">\n\t\t    <NOT <==? ,HERE ,YOUR-ROOM>>>\n\t       <RFALSE>)\n\t      (<VERB? FOLLOW>\n\t       <RFALSE>)\n\t      (T <RTRUE>)>)\n       (<T? ,GENDER-KNOWN>\n\t<COND (<==? .PER ,DEB>\n\t       <COND (<NOT <FSET? ,PLAYER ,FEMALE>>\n\t\t      <RTRUE>)\n\t\t     (T <RFALSE>)>)\n\t      (<==? .PER ,OFFICER>\n\t       <COND (<FSET? ,PLAYER ,FEMALE>\n\t\t      <RTRUE>)\n\t\t     (T <RFALSE>)>)\n\t      (T <RFALSE>)>)>>"
