   "source": "<ROUTINE WINNER-DEFAULT (PER)\n\t<COND (<T? ,GENDER-KNOWN>\n\t       <TELL !\\\">\n\t       <COND (<T? ,FAWNING> <TELL \"But \">)>\n\t       <TELL \"I really can't help you with that\">\n\t       <COND (<EQUAL? .PER ,OFFICER>\n\t\t      <IAN-CALLS-YOU>)>\n\t       <TELL \".\\\"\" CR>)\n\t      (T <WHY-ME> <RFATAL>)>>"
